{
    "content": "<div style='display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;'><img src='../img/server.png' alt='zeek' style='width: 100px; height: 100px;'></div> <div style='padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;'><font color='teal'><h3>Zeek</h3></font></div>",
    "depth": 1,
    "children": [
        {
            "content": "<h4>开源的网络流量分析工具</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "区别于传统防火墙、IDS、IPS, Zeek 更聚焦在为用户提供对网络流量的获取、表达及分析的能力上",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "将获取到的网络流量转化成格式化的文本, 即 Zeek 日志",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "提供一套具有图灵完备性的编程语言—— Zeek 脚本",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "主要提供对 OSI 中网络层至应用层协议的流量分析能力",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "4.0 即之后的版本新增了包分析框架, 从而使得 Zeek 具有了分析数据链路层数据帧的能力",
                            "depth": 3
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "但相关的内置分析脚本还不丰富, 分析手段也较为简单",
                            "depth": 3
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>部署使用</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "基于标准 libpcap 接口获取流量包",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "核心代码: C++",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "仅支持在类 UNIX 操作系统中（包括 Linux、FreeBSD 及 macOS）运行",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "支持单点部署及集群式部署, 并提供配套的集群管理工具 ZeekControl",
                    "depth": 3
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "command",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "<code><b>zeek [options] [file ...]</b></code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-a|--parse-only</code> 脚本解析后直接退出",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-b|--bare-mode</code> 不载入内置的协议分析脚本",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-e|--exec [zeek code]</code> 执行脚本 e.g. 'print \"Hello World!\";'",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-f|--filter [filter] 过滤规则 e.g. 'port 80'</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-i|--iface [interface]</code> 网络接口",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-p|--prefix [prefix]</code> 同时加载前缀为 prefix. 的文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-r|--readfile [readfile]</code> 读取 pcap 文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-s|--rulefile [rulefile]</code> 特征文件(signature, .sig 文件)",
                            "depth": 4,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<code>e.g.<br>signature test-signature {<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;ip-proto == tcp<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;dst-port = 80<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;payload .*passwd/ <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;event \"payload of dst-port=80/tcp contains 'passwd'\"<br>}</code>",
                                    "depth": 5
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-v|--version</code> 版本号",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-w|--writefile [writefile]</code> 分析流量的同时将流量数据包写入文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-C|--no-checksums</code> 关闭对数据包校验和的检查",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-D|--deterministic</code> 关闭随时生成 uid 的功能",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-G|--load-seeds [file]</code> 载入随机数种子文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-H|--save-seeds [file]</code> 保存随机数种子文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-I|--print-id [ID name]</code> 某个脚本变量的类型定义",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-N|--print-plugins</code> 已加载的插件信息",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-X|--zeekygen</code> 生成 Zeek 脚本相关注释",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "<code><b>zeekctl</b></code>",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "<code><b>zeek-cut [options] [columns]</b></code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-c</code> 显示日志文件头部以 # 开头的日志元数据部分",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-C</code> 显示日志文件所有以 # 开头的日志元数据部分",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-d</code> 将时间字段 ts 转换为易于阅读的格式并显示",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-D [fmt]</code> 将时间字段 ts 转换为 [fmt] 指定的格式(参考 strftime())并显示",
                            "depth": 4,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "content": "e.g. %Y-%m-%d",
                                    "depth": 5
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-F [ofs]</code> 将日志中字段间的分隔符转换为参数给定的符号",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-h</code> 帮助信息",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-n</code> 显示日志中除给定字段外的其它所有字段",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-u</code> 与 <code>-d</code> 相似, 但采用 UTC 时间",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-U [fmt]</code>, 与 <code>-D</code> 相似, 但采用 UTC 时间",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>可视化方案(Ubuntu) ELK</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "<b>Elasticsearch 8.X</b>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "home: <code>/usr/share/elasticsearch</code><br> service: <code>/lib/systemd/system/elasticsearch.service</code> (其中设置了环境变量, <code>sudo systemctl start elasticsearch</code>)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "data: <code>/var/lib/elasticsearch</code><br> logs: <code>/var/log/elasticsearch</code><br> config: <code>/etc/elasticsearch</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "visit: <code>https://ip:port</code>(ip 和 port 在 config 中设置, port 默认 9200, 超级用户为 elastic, 密码在安装时自动生成)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Reset the password of the elastic built-in superuser with <code>/usr/share/elasticsearch/bin/elasticsearch-reset-password -u elastic</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "查看索引: <code>https://ip:port/_cat/indices</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "<b>Kibana 8.X</b>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "home: <code>/usr/share/kibana</code><br> service: <code>/lib/systemd/system/kibana.service</code> (其中设置了环境变量, <code>sudo systemctl start kibana</code>)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "data: <code>/var/lib/kibana</code><br> logs: <code>/var/log/kibana</code><br> config: <code>/etc/kibana</code><br>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "visit: <code>http://ip:port</code>(监听地址、端口在 config 中设置, port 默认 5601)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "汉化: 在 kibana.yml 中加入 <code>i18n.locale: \"zh-CN\"</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "<b>Filebeat 8.X</b>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "home: <code>/usr/share/filebeat</code><br> service: <code>/lib/systemd/system/filebeat.service</code> (其中设置了环境变量, <code>sudo systemctl start filebeat</code>)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "data: <code>/var/lib/filebeat</code><br> config: <code>/etc/filebeat</code><br> model: <code>/etc/filebeat/modules.d</code> (e.g. zeek.yml)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "启动 zeek 模块 <br><code>sudo filebeat modules enable zeek</code><br><code>sudo filebeat setup</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "<b>Logstash 8.X (Filebeat 8.X 直接传输到 ES, 难以改为通过 Logstash 再传输到 ES)</b>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "home: <code>/usr/share/logstash</code><br> service: <code>/lib/systemd/system/logstash.service</code> (其中设置了环境变量, <code>sudo systemctl start logstash</code>)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "data: <code>/var/lib/logstash</code><br> logs: <code>/var/log/logstash</code><br> config: <code>/etc/logstash</code>)",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>[PREFIX]/bin/logstash -f /etc/filebeat/filebeat.conf</code>(默认端口 5044)",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>打流</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "<b><a href='https://github.com/esnet/iperf'>iperf</a></b>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "QA",
                            "depth": 4,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "content": "Q1: error - unable to connect to server - server may have stopped running or use a different port, firewall issue, etc.: Connection refused",
                                    "depth": 5
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "A1: 更新防火墙设置, 打开对应的端口, 使得对应的流量可以通过网关到达服务器 <code>sudo ufw allow [端口号]/[协议]</code>",
                                    "depth": 5
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Server: <code>iperf3 -s -p [port]</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Client: <code>iperf3 -c [ip] -p [port]</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>发现网络资产(<code>[PREFIX]/share/zeek/policy/</code> 下以 <code>know</code> 开头的脚本) </h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "主机 <code>[PREFIX]/share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-hosts.zeek</code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "主机地址:<br>· <code>ALL_HOSTS</code> 所有地址 <br>· <code>LOCAL_HOSTS</code> 本地地址(可在 <code>[PREFIX]/etc/networks.cfg</code> 中自定义) <br>· <code>REMOTE_HOSTS</code> 除本地地址外的所有地址 <br>· <code>NO_HOSTS<code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>sudo bin/zeek -b -i ens33 -C share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-hosts.zeek -e 'redef Known::host_tracking = ALL_HOSTS;'</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "字段: ts, host",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>cat known_hosts.log | zeek-cut -d</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "服务 <code>[PREFIX]/share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-services.zeek</code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code>sudo bin/zeek -i ens33 -C share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-services.zeek -e 'redef Known::service_tracking = ALL_HOSTS;'</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "字段: ts, host, port_num, port_proto, service",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>cat known_services.log | zeek-cut -d</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "流量中传输的证书 <code>[PREFIX]/share/zeek/policy/protocols/ssl/known-certs.zeek</code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code>sudo bin/zeek -i ens33 -C share/zeek/policy/protocols/ssl/known-certs.zeek</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "字段: ts, uid, id.orig_h, id.orig_p, id.resp_h, id.resp_p, version, cipher, curve, server_name, resumed last_alert, next_protocol, established, ssl_history, cert_chain_fps, client_cert_chain_fps, sni_matches_cert",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>cat ssl.log | zeek-cut -d</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "Modbus 协议中 Master 节点及 Slave 节点 <code>[PREFIX]/share/zeek/policy/protocols/modbus/known-master-slaves.zeek</code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
